title: Rejection Note
description: निर्दिष्ट करता है behavior on Rejection Note Stored

title: Rejection Note Code
description: निर्दिष्ट करता है Document Title of Rejection Note इस फॉर्मेट में (CV, CSD, 'CM')

title: Accept Previous Rejected Instance
description: निर्दिष्ट करता है behavior on subsequent occurrence of instances rejected by a particular Rejection Note.

title: Overwrite Previous Rejection
description: निर्दिष्ट करता है Document Title of previous Rejection Note इस फॉर्मेट में (CV, CSD, 'CM') which may be overwritten by that Rejection Note

title: Accept Rejection before Storage
description: Time interval in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में after receive of a Rejection Note, in which received object referenced by this Rejection Note are treated as rejected. Referenced objects received afterwards are treated as subsequent occurrence of an already rejected instance. If not present, Rejection Notes which refers not yet received objects will not be accepted.

title: Delete Rejected Instance Delay
description: Delay in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में after which instances rejected by a particular Rejection Note are deleted. Infinite if absent.

title: Delete Rejection Note Delay
description: Delay in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में after which particular Rejection Notes are deleted. Infinite if absent.
